AUTH_JWT_SECRET|string|required|32+ random chars|JWT secret explícito da UI
EXOCORTEX_ADMIN_PASSWORD|string|required|generated local secret|Senha do super_admin bootstrapado
EXOCORTEX_HERMES_WEB_UI_REF|string|required|git ref, tag ou commit|Pin do upstream
EXOCORTEX_HERMES_HOME|path|required|persistent volume|Runtime Hermes persistente
EXOCORTEX_HOME|path|required|persistent volume|Workspace cognitivo persistente
EXOCORTEX_WEB_UI_HOME|path|required|persistent volume|Estado da UI, DB, logs e uploads
